    options: ["Report the fire, Alarm activation, Contain the area, Evacuate all patients and personnel safely", "Respond to the alarm, Alert charge nurse, Close all fire doors, Exit via designated evacuation routes", "Rescue endangered persons, Alarm activation, Contain/Confine the fire, Extinguish or Evacuate appropriately", "React to the situation, Assess the fire size, Call the fire department, Extinguish if safely possible"],
