    options: ["Hazardous waste containers should be sealed and replaced when they reach the three-quarters full level", "Fill levels for hazardous waste containers are not specifically regulated — replacement follows a scheduled basis", "Container replacement is required only when the container has reached its completely full maximum capacity", "Containers may be filled to maximum capacity as long as the lid mechanism still closes and latches securely"],
