    options: ["Sharps containers must be positioned at a height accessible to staff without reaching above shoulder level", "This is acceptable practice if the facility provides step stools at each sharps container station location", "Wall-mounted sharps container height is universally standardized and acceptable for all staff members", "Container mounting height requirements apply only to sharps containers installed in patient room locations"],
