    options: ["Initial orientation is the only required safety training element for employees during their first year", "Additional safety training is required exclusively for employees assigned to designated high-risk departments", "The frequency of safety training beyond orientation is determined by the employee's annual performance review", "Ongoing safety education and annual competency verification are required beyond the initial orientation training"],
